"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWURfu7Lk3xJ1/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/lofi-mediation-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/lofi-mediation-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY" data-swiper-slide-index="2"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWSADWNdZfn11/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/relaxing-piano-covers-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/relaxing-piano-covers-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY" data-swiper-slide-index="3"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWXe9gFZP0gtP/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/stress-relief-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/stress-relief-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY" data-swiper-slide-index="4"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWUZ5bk6qqDSy/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/white-noise-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/white-noise-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY" data-swiper-slide-index="5"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DX65caF1CvtIN/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/piano-for-healing-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/piano-for-healing-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY swiper-slide-duplicate" data-swiper-slide-index="0"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWZqd5JICZI0u/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/peaceful-meditation-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/peaceful-meditation-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY swiper-slide-duplicate" data-swiper-slide-index="1"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWURfu7Lk3xJ1/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/lofi-mediation-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/lofi-mediation-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY swiper-slide-duplicate" data-swiper-slide-index="2"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWSADWNdZfn11/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/relaxing-piano-covers-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/relaxing-piano-covers-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY swiper-slide-duplicate" data-swiper-slide-index="3"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWXe9gFZP0gtP/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/stress-relief-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/stress-relief-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY swiper-slide-duplicate" data-swiper-slide-index="4"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWUZ5bk6qqDSy/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/white-noise-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/white-noise-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_thumbnail__CgWRY swiper-slide-duplicate" data-swiper-slide-index="5"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div><a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/37i9dQZF1DX65caF1CvtIN/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img class="thumbnailcard_image__ApqRB" src="/images/120x120/piano-for-healing-240.jpg" alt="/images/120x120/piano-for-healing-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="mental-health-three-pillars" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-m mb-mobile-m"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Our approach</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>With Heart & Soul, we aim to do three things. We believe all need to co-exist to make a meaningful impact on our culture and our people.</p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-l mb-mobile-l"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 mb-mobile-s col-offset-2 col-10" style="display:flex;order:1"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>Everything we do connects back to this strategy. Since launching in 2018, Heart & Soul has focused on providing moments for our band members to build their knowledge around mental health and mental illness. </p><p>Since our experiences of both are unique, we also aim to give our people the tools and resources they need to nurture their mental health in their own way.</p></div><a href="https://www.lifeatspotify.com/reports/Heart-And-Soul-Under-The-Spotlight-Report-2022.pdf" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="fw-normal size-6 size-8-mobile no-underline color-ui-black links_linkArrow__Woina links_light__IjDhd mt-xs">Heart &amp; Soul Under The Spotlight report</a></div></div><div class="col-8 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 mb-mobile-m col-offset-2" style="align-self:flex-end"><div class="mb-s mb-mobile-xs"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile p-relative statcard_container__NxqMx bg-light-green statcard_noBorder__eKMrR"><p class="fw-normal line-110 line-120-mobile ma-0 statcard_value__eeVmR undefined size-3">1.</p><p class="fw-light size-8-mobile line-150 ma-0 statcard_label__2U_24 undefined size-6">Raise awareness and build knowledge.</p></div></div><div class="mb-s mb-mobile-xs"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile p-relative statcard_container__NxqMx bg-light-green statcard_noBorder__eKMrR"><p class="fw-normal line-110 line-120-mobile ma-0 statcard_value__eeVmR undefined size-3">2.</p><p class="fw-light size-8-mobile line-150 ma-0 statcard_label__2U_24 undefined size-6">Enable proactive self-care and professional support.</p></div></div><div class="mb-s mb-mobile-xs"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile p-relative statcard_container__NxqMx bg-light-green statcard_noBorder__eKMrR"><p class="fw-normal line-110 line-120-mobile ma-0 statcard_value__eeVmR undefined size-3">3.</p><p class="fw-light size-8-mobile line-150 ma-0 statcard_label__2U_24 undefined size-6">Normalize the conversation surrounding mental health to reduce stigma.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-m mb-mobile-m"><div class="row mb-xxs mb-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-6 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-3 line-110 bg-color-active">Our ambassadors are at the heart of this work</h2></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-5 line-150 size-7-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-6 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>Three pillars may help us to focus our efforts, but Heart & Soul cannot truly thrive without the help of others.</p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-l mb-mobile-0"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>A healthy and supportive environment is created from the inside – any meaningful change needs to be driven by and together with band members. That’s why we introduced mental health ambassadors, employees from across Spotify who devote a few hours per week to spreading the Heart & Soul message, planning and driving initiatives, and ensuring activities are approached in a locally-relevant way.</p><p>When an ever-increasing number of band members reached out to ambassadors for guidance and advice – we listened – sending our team of volunteers to train as Mental Health First Aiders.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-9 col-offset-2 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/strategy-to-life-1.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Since 2021, they’ve been equipped to facilitate supportive conversations, listen in a non-judgmental way and guide band members towards the right support – whether that’s self-care tools and resources, or therapy.</p><p>Our ambassadors’ dedication to creating a culture that allows people to speak up and take good care of themselves is undeniable. The whole team can feel the impact they have, and we can say from the bottom of our hearts that they’re instrumental in helping us to create a supportive and stigma-free culture. Spotify provides the guidance and the framework, but it’s our ambassadors who breathe life into Heart & Soul. </p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-9 col-offset-2 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/strategy-to-life-2.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div></section><section id="all-the-feels" class="layout-section py-section bg-light-green pt-50% pb-mobile-ml LayoutSection_topImageBg__PEXrI"><div id="mentalhealth-animation-trigger" class="mentalhealthanimation_absoluteContainer__sOc3b"><div class="mentalhealthanimation_relativeContainer__SSRjB"><div id="leftCloud" class="mentalhealthanimation_leftCloud__szs_b"><img src="/esg-animation/MentalHealth/left-cloud.svg" alt="left-cloud"/></div><div id="rightCloud" class="mentalhealthanimation_rightCloud__zPe8U"><img src="/esg-animation/MentalHealth/right-cloud.svg" alt="left-cloud"/></div><div id="sun" class="mentalhealthanimation_sun__2vP1g"><img src="/esg-animation/MentalHealth/sun.svg" alt="left-cloud"/></div><div id="mainCloud" class="mentalhealthanimation_mainCloud__iIgau"><img src="/esg-animation/MentalHealth/main-cloud.svg" alt="left-cloud"/></div></div></div><div class="rounded-20 bg-white pt-l pb-l pt-mobile-l pb-mobile-l pl-mobile-0 pr-mobile-0 mr-m ml-m mr-mobile-xs ml-mobile-xs p-relative mb-mobile-xl bigcontentblock_container__5AMaV"><div class="container block-container mb-m mb-mobile-m"><div class="row mb-xxs mb-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-6 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-3 line-110 bg-color-active">All the feels</h2></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-5 line-150 size-7-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-6 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>Stigma grows in silence. We aim to combat it by making help and support more accessible.</p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>We want to make it easier for our listeners and creators to get the support they need for themselves or others they know who are struggling. We help by offering short-term counseling – available 24/7 – through our All The Feels program and by hosting an easy-to-navigate microsite full of localized resources.</p></div><a href="https://resources.byspotify.com/" aria-label="Mental health resources" class="size-7 size-8-mobile fw-normal clear-button buttons_filled__uuK0X mt-xs">Mental health resources</a></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-9 col-offset-2 my-auto"><picture><source srcSet="/images/413x580/M&amp;H_all_the_feels-434.webp" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/M&amp;H_all_the_feels-434.jpg" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/M&amp;H_all_the_feels-826.webp" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/413x580/M&amp;H_all_the_feels-826.jpg" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/jpeg"/><img src="/images/413x580/M&amp;H_all_the_feels-826.jpg" alt="" style="max-width:414px;max-height:580px" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_image__nIttw textimage_imageLargeMobile__vDuBQ"/></picture></div></div></div></div></section><section id="domestic-abuse-program" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-m mb-mobile-m"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Recognising and responding to abuse at home</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>We believe that everybody has a vital role to play in preventing and tackling domestic abuse. </p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>That’s why we’ve extended our Heart & Soul initiative to also provide help for any band members experiencing abuse at home and to raise awareness more generally.</p><p>Band members can access a library of resources to help build their knowledge and understanding, and we aim to offer immediate support to anyone affected, promoting their safety, wellbeing and reducing disruption to their lives at work.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-9 col-offset-2 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/domestic-abuse-program.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div></section><section id="partnering-up" class="layout-section py-section pt-mobile-ml pb-mobile-ml"><div class="container block-container mb-l mb-mobile-l"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-12 text-center-mobile"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-2 line-120">Partnering up</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>We can’t drive meaningful change on our own. We collaborate closely with external partners who act as a sounding board for our initiatives and support our band members with various programs.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-offset-1 col-8 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/partnering-up.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU carousel_has-fadeUp-outside__Ts9NF container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><div class="text-center mb-s mb-mobile-xs"><div class="tags_container__mE0BD tags_light-orange__cGOiO"><p class="ma-0 size-7 size-9-mobile fw-normal">Communities</p></div></div><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">Supporting our communities</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm"><p>Our mental health partners are here to enhance the support we offer. One example of how they help is Heart & Soul Community Circles. The purpose of a Circle is to boost social support within the workplace through education, reflection, connection and providing practical tools - all centred around a specific mental health topic. Our Circles are always hosted by external mental health professionals, who help choose the topic that’s relevant to that specific community, at that specific point in time.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="popup_container__EMIkb" style="visibility:hidden"><div class="popup_inner__wgnJ3"><div class="popup_closeContainer__V1wpI"><button aria-label="Close" class="clear-button popup_close__zlFgp"></button></div><div class="rounded-20 popup_content__8nEU9"><div class=""><div class="text-center mb-s mb-mobile-xs"><div class="tags_container__mE0BD tags_light-orange__cGOiO"><p class="ma-0 size-7 size-9-mobile fw-normal">Ambassador circles</p></div></div><p class="ma-0 mb-m mb-mobile-xxs fw-normal size-4 size-6-mobile line-120 text-center">Supporting our Ambassadors</p><div class="size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 link-light-bg popupcontent_body__pVJgm"><p>Partners also work closely with our Heart & Soul Ambassadors, equipping them to support their colleagues while also taking care of themselves. Every month, we offer Ambassador Circles, one-hour sessions that explore a specific mental health area through education, reflection, conversation and hands-on resources. Ambassador Circles offer our Ambassadors – who are so often focused on the mental health of others – an opportunity and space to tune into themselves.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Supporting our communities</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Our mental health partners are here to enhance the support we offer and help facilitate tailored initiatives for our many Communities.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_wide__Bg_wd"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_cursor__wvFAi clear-button defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_wide__2Gt4v defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Supporting our Ambassadors</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez">Partners also work closely with our Heart &amp; Soul Ambassadors, equipping them to support their colleagues while also taking care of themselves.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop defaultcard_hasCta__YfZqx"></span><p class="size-6 size-8-mobile ma-0 no-underline fw-normal color-white bottomlink_container__NPBGI bottomlink_plus__3w8tn bottomlink_link___hzIf">Learn more</p></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="layout-section py-section"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24"><h2 class="bg-color-active line-110 size-3 text-center mb-m mb-mobile-m">Quick clicks</h2><a class="mb-xs mb-mobile-xs quicklink_container__XU717" href="/diversity-equity-impact/climate-action"><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-visible-desktop is-hidden-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">Discover more about <span>Climate Action</span></p><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-hidden-desktop is-visible-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds"><span>Climate Action</span></p><div class="quicklink_button__B3y8U"><button aria-label="Go to page" style="transform:rotate(nulldeg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_dark__M7afL undefined arrows_darkBackground__ZtZM9"></button></div></a><a class="mb-xs mb-mobile-xs quicklink_container__XU717" href="/diversity-equity-impact/diversity-equity-inclusion-belonging"><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-visible-desktop is-hidden-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">See our <span>Diversity, Equity & Inclusion</span> initiatives</p><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-hidden-desktop is-visible-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">About <span>belonging</span></p><div class="quicklink_button__B3y8U"><button aria-label="Go to page" style="transform:rotate(nulldeg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_dark__M7afL undefined arrows_darkBackground__ZtZM9"></button></div></a><a class="mb-xs mb-mobile-xs quicklink_container__XU717" href="/diversity-equity-impact/social-impact"><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-visible-desktop is-hidden-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds">Read about <span>Social Impact</span></p><p class="ma-0 color-gray-400 is-hidden-desktop is-visible-mobile bg-color-active size-4 size-6-mobile line-140 quicklink_text__fQxds"><span>Social impact</span></p><div class="quicklink_button__B3y8U"><button aria-label="Go to page" style="transform:rotate(nulldeg)" class="arrows_filled__L4ANR arrows_dark__M7afL undefined arrows_darkBackground__ZtZM9"></button></div></a></div></div></div></section></main><footer id="js-footer" class="footer_container__5R4W_"><div class="container p-relative color-white"><div class="is-hidden-mobile footer_s